'''Hira Mani''' ({{lang-ur|{{Nastaliq| حرا مانی‬‎}}}}) is husband and wife team of Salman Saquib Sheikh ({{lang-ur|{{Nastaliq| شيخ سلمان ثاقب }}}}), known as ''Mani'' and Hira Salman ({{lang-ur|{{Nastaliq| حرا سلمان‬‎}}}}), known as ''Hira'', are Pakistani actors, television hosts, and VJ duo.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://tribune.com.pk/story/1650803/4-im-proud-labelled-manis-wife-hira-mani/|title=I'm proud to be labelled Mani's wife|work=The Express Tribune|accessdate=13 April 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.pakistantoday.com.pk/2015/06/06/entertainment/telenor-bridal-couture-week-kicks-off-in-style/|title=Telenor Bridal Couture Week kicks off in style|work=Pakistan Today|date=6 June 2015|accessdate=27 September 2015|quote=Acclaimed actor Mansha Pasha walked for Telenor Karo Mumkin collection by Ayesha Ibrahim, the young Suhai Ali Abro walked for Shazia Kiyani, the graceful Zhyalay Sarhadi wore the showstopper for Sana Abbas; Hira, Mani, Saim and Sana Fakher donned the showstoppers for Goal by Fozia Ahmed...}}</ref><ref name="ET">{{cite news|url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/664904/azfar-and-mani-bury-the-hatchet-for-sab-set-hai-too/|title=Azfar and Mani bury the hatchet for Sab Set Hai Too|work=The Express Tribune|date=29 January 2014|accessdate=27 September 2015|first=Rafay|last=Mahmood}}</ref>
